@startuml seq_10_create_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-10 Create Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Community Repo" as CommRepo
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Event Bus\n(Go Channels)" as EventBus

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open Create Post modal
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Select a community
User -> Frontend: (3.1) Choose post type and enter title/content
User -> Frontend: (4.1) Attach media or configure poll if needed
User -> Frontend: (5.1) Submit the post
Frontend -> Controller: (5.2) POST /api/posts (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: (6.1) Create post request
Service -> CommRepo: (6.2) Validate author and community membership
CommRepo --> Service: (6.3) Membership valid

alt Media files attached
    Service -> Cloudinary: (8.1) Upload media stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: (8.2) Return media URLs and IDs
end

Service -> PostRepo: (7.1) Create post record
PostRepo --> Service: (7.2) Post created (ID)

Service -> EventBus: (10.1) Trigger moderation workflow
note right of EventBus
  Background goroutines handle 
  moderation and notifications
end note

Service --> Controller: (10.2) Created post data
Controller --> Frontend: (10.3) 201 Created
Frontend --> User: (10.4) Redirect to new post
@enduml
